Class ClusMog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.tests.memorydb.ClusMog
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClusMogSQL

    public class ClusMog
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple utility to compute/recover the parameters of a mixture-of-Gaussian distribution from independent samples.

      • cluster

        public void cluster(int n,
                    double[] center,
                    int ns,
                    double[] sample)
        Compute/recover the parameters of a mixture-of-Gaussian distribution from given independent samples.
        Parameters:
        n - number of clusters (Gaussian components) to output
        center - initial cluster centers for iterative refinement
        ns - number of input samples
        sample - input samples; will be sorted in ascending order during use
